Charles Sutton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Sutton 0 Charles Sutton (1856 – July 20, 1935) was an American film actor of the silent era. He appeared in over one hundred films between 1911 and 1923. He died in Englewood, New Jersey. Charles_Sutton ( 1856 – July_20_,_1935 ) was an_American_film_actor of the_silent_era .
